snippet: Creighton coach Greg McDermott knew the No. 10 Bluejays got away with one after they lost a 13-point second-half lead, didn't score in the final 3:28 and still managed to beat Oral Roberts 66-65 on Saturday night....
lead_paragraph: Creighton coach Greg McDermott knew the No. 10 Bluejays got away with one after they lost a 13-point second-half lead, didn't score in the final 3:28 and still managed to beat Oral Roberts 66-65 on Saturday night.

headline.main: Foster Has 22 Points, Creighton Rallies to Beat Oral Roberts
headline.print_headline: Foster Has 22 Points, Creighton Rallies to Beat Oral Roberts
